        {
          "character": "田大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你就要来吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（田大下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李三春",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈，我在那刚一打你，你就把我们大哥给弄来啦。我还是那一句话，你要不"
        },
        {
          "character": "李三春",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "保佑着我们分了家，我一天还是打你个七八遍。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（小鬼看。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李三春",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳，可气死我了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李三春捽棍，下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "灶君",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "李氏三春太不良，终朝每日打灶王。明日上殿奏一本，叫她师傅屁股眼下长大"
        },
        {
          "character": "灶君",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "疮！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（灶君、小鬼同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "李三春→田大",
          "turns": 5
        },
        {
          "edge": "田大→李三春",
          "turns": 5
        },
        {
          "edge": "李三春→灶君",
          "turns": 1
        }
      ],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
