    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "李三春",
        "田二",
        "田大",
        "田大妻"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（田大、田大妻同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "田大",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "读书求功名，"
        },
        {
          "character": "田大妻",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "拜佛念经文。"
        },
        {
          "character": "田大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今有三弟妹，清晨起来，打骂灶君，不知为了何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "田大妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待我唤她出来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "田大妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三弟妹哪里？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李三春",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李三春上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李三春",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "忽听兄嫂唤，迈步到跟前。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李三春",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大哥、大嫂子。"
        },
        {
          "character": "田大、田大妻",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三弟妹，清晨早起，打骂灶君，不知为了何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李三春",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大哥、大嫂子有所不知，只因咱们这个日子，实实难过。我这个家，也真是当"
        },
        {
          "character": "李三春",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不了啦。我想要分居另过。"
        },
        {
          "character": "田大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三弟妹说哪里话来。常言道得好："
        },
        {
          "character": "田大",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "分居不胜同居好，大家捧柴火焰高。"
        },
        {
          "character": "田大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "张公艺九世同居，世间少有。兄有一言，你且听了："
        },
        {
          "character": "田大",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "三弟妹休得要闹吵吵，"
        },
        {
          "character": "田大",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "愚兄言来听根苗："
        },
        {
          "character": "田大",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "大家捧柴火焰高。"
        },
        {
          "character": "田大",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "分家不如同居好"
        },
        {
          "character": "李三春",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大哥这个话，你也不要再说啦。我的心思是一定啦。你若分给我便罢，如若不"
        },
        {
          "character": "李三春",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "然，我就与你天天吵，天天闹。"
        },
        {
          "character": "田二",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓哈！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（田二上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "田二",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "太爷退堂出衙道，"
        },
        {
          "character": "田二",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "急忙回家看根苗。"
        },
        {
          "character": "田二",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "一脚门里一脚门外"
        },
        {
          "character": "李三春",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你要是不分给我，我就与你天天吵，天天闹。"
        },
        {
          "character": "田二",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "田二",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "又听得三弟妹乱七八糟。"
        },
        {
          "character": "田二",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我说大哥呀，今个大清早起，你把三弟妹，弄得这么鸡毛子喊叫，到底是为的"
        },
        {
          "character": "田二",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "什么事下？"
        },
        {
          "character": "田大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二弟，你回来了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "田二",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我回来啦。我早就回来啦。到底三弟妹这是为什么呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "田大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三弟妹要分家。"
        },
        {
          "character": "田二",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "她要分家，你就该去劝她才是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "田大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "愚兄再三相劝，她执意不听也是枉然。"
        },
        {
          "character": "田二",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你是什么也不能干，你瞧我的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "田大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你去劝来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "田二",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我说三弟妹，愚兄这儿有礼啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李三春",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢啦，你才下学吗？"
        },
        {
          "character": "田大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "田二",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你得啦！我这受着热呐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "田二",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三弟妹，你可是真不对。哥哥在这与你施礼，你怎么说才下学呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李三春",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今个是年下啦？"
        },
        {
          "character": "田二",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不是呀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李三春",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是过节？"
        },
        {
          "character": "田二",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "也不是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李三春",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一不是年，二不是节，你作的什么揖呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "田二",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不错。我这叫做礼多人不怪。我且问你：大清早起，你吵吵闹闹，莫非是咱们"
        },
        {
          "character": "田二",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大哥得罪你啦？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李三春",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我们大哥，是个读书的人，他怎么会得罪着我？不是的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "田二",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦。是咱们大嫂子得罪着你啦？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李三春",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你说是咱们大嫂子得罪着我？你想她是个吃斋念佛的人，除了烧香，就是磕头，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李三春",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将来人家想上西天呐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "田二",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "对啦，上西天，可别上冬天，冬天还靡有皮袄啦！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李三春",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不是的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "田二",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那么莫非是我得罪你啦么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李三春",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二哥你是衙门里头出来进去这么一个粉红头儿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "田二",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "头儿就得啦，别上颜色啦！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李三春",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你是天天不在家，你怎么也得罪不了我。不是的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "田二",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是啦，必是你二嫂子得罪了你啦。如果是她，等我打她一顿，给你出出气。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李三春",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得啦，得啦！你别说啦！有一天我打你们房门口过，听见里头吵吵闹闹，我把"
        },
        {
          "character": "李三春",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "窗户纸捅破了一个小窟窿一看，你给二嫂子那儿跪着呐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "田二",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你哪儿知道，我是掉在炉火坑里啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李三春",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我们二嫂子，还是气得呼吓呼吓地生气呐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "田二",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你不知道，那是我教她吹唢呐换气啦。你不生气，愚兄有一言，你且听了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "田二",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "三弟妹不必怒冲霄，"
        },
        {
          "character": "田二",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "细听二哥说根苗："
        },
        {
          "character": "田二",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "大家捧柴火焰高。"
        },
        {
          "character": "田二",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "分家不如同居好"
        },
        {
          "character": "李三春",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这几句话人家早说过了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "田二",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪个王八蛋说过了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "田大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李三春",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大哥说过啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "田二",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我看你是好说不成，我简直告诉你说，你不听话，二哥今个要管教管教你。我"
        },
        {
          "character": "田二",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "要打你！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李三春",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好，你要打，你来罢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "田大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二弟万万使不得。"
        },
        {
          "character": "田二",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你不要管，我的气上来，王八蛋也挡不住。你招打！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李三春坐。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李三春",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我说东邻呐，西舍呀！我们当家的不在家，他们两个大伯子，在这里争风呐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李三春",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好，你们来罢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "田二",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大哥你去罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "田大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳，不要胡说。看她既是这样吵闹，你我就将家私分与了她罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "田二",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好，分就分了罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "田大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三弟妹不要动怒，将家私分与你就是了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李三春",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好，分给我啦。分给我，我就不闹了。嗳呀，大哥，你回避回避。二哥，你也"
        },
        {
          "character": "李三春",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "掉过去，我们这儿一生气，把裤腰带撑断啦。我说你们大家都看看，我但凡有"
        },
        {
          "character": "李三春",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一根整裤腰带，我也不分这个家。"
        },
        {
          "character": "田二",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你那是说瞎话呐。你里头不是系着花汗巾吗？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李三春",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我们走啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "田大",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "分了罢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "田二",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "分了罢！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖牌子〗。众人同下。）"
